Using URLs by these form doesn&#x27;t work:

* {{[Link Text](URL)}}
* {{[Link Text][1]}}, and {{[1]: https://...}}

For example, here is in issue description: [Bitbucket|https://bitbucket.org].

I&#x27;ll post one comment then.

Bug can be reproduced by following the steps below:

# {code}
  Go to https://bitbucket.org/{team}
{code}
# {code}
  Click on the top left “Edit avatar”
{code}
# {code}
  Click on “Select an image” (browse for the image)
{code}
# {code}
  Click on “Save”
{code}

This only happens if the name of the team is numeric.

For example this HTML code renders code tag with corresponding header font size:

{code}
:::html
<h1>This is H1 with <code>Java code</code></h1>
{code}

However this markdown code renders code block with normal font size:

{code}
:::markdown
# This is H1 with `Java code`
{code}

For instance:

h1. This is H1 with {{Java code}}
Please fix this...

Thank you.
